**Testing Protocol:**
- Test in the morning (8-10am) when T peaks
- Fast 12 hours
- No heavy training day before
- No alcohol 48 hours before

**When These Markers Drift Off:**
When your physique starts looking "flat" or "watery" despite good diet and training, these markers usually explain why.

**What to Do If Markers Are Off:**
1. Optimize lifestyle first (sleep, stress, nutrition)
2. Retest in 8-12 weeks
3. If still off, consult with an endocrinologist or hormone specialist
4. Don't jump to TRT without trying lifestyle optimization first`,
